name: LikesPro.com
overview:
LikesPro is created to help Facebook page administrators steadily gain thousands of Facebook Likes fast for FREE! Simply Like a bunch of Facebook pages and others will Like your Facebook page back.

LikesPro places your Facebook Account in front of thousands of real people legitimately interested in your individual, business, product or service. With LikesPro you can easily find interesting accounts to Like, while you grow your own number of likes by thousands daily!
